Text: Haas web services page now available and welcome back to Haas The Haas Marketing and Communications Web Team is happy to present a new web page for you At groupsWebteamsetuphtml youll find information about the Haas web site and about maintaining your own Haas web pages Of particular interest may be the Haas How do I web page at groupsWebteamhowdoihtml directing students faculty members and staff members to various web development resources As with all web pages this is a forevergrowing module so watch for new additions as the year grows older Debra Debra Goldentyer Web Editor Haas School of Business University of California Berkeley E Student Services Building Mail Student Services Berkeley California Phone Fax Email atthtm
